vernac_cmds: Inductive t : Type := Nil | Cons (lo hi: Z) (tl: t).
Fixpoint In (x: Z) (s: t) := match s with | Nil => False | Cons l h s' => l <= x < h \/ In x s' end.
Inductive ok: t -> Prop := | ok_nil: ok Nil | ok_cons: forall l h s (BOUNDS: l < h) (BELOW: forall x, In x s -> h < x) (OK: ok s), ok (Cons l h s).
Fixpoint mem (x: Z) (s: t) : bool := match s with | Nil => false | Cons l h s' => if zlt x h then zle l x else mem x s' end.
Lemma mem_In: forall x s, ok s -> (mem x s = true <-> In x s).
Fixpoint contains (L H: Z) (s: t) : bool := match s with | Nil => false | Cons l h s' => (zle H h && zle l L) || contains L H s' end.
Lemma contains_In: forall l0 h0, l0 < h0 -> forall s, ok s -> (contains l0 h0 s = true <-> (forall x, l0 <= x < h0 -> In x s)).

Fixpoint add (L H: Z) (s: t) {struct s} : t := match s with | Nil => Cons L H Nil | Cons l h s' => if zlt h L then Cons l h (add L H s') else if zlt H l then Cons L H s else add (Z.min l L) (Z.max h H) s' end.
Lemma In_add: forall x s, ok s -> forall l0 h0, (In x (add l0 h0 s) <-> l0 <= x < h0 \/ In x s).
assert (l0 <= x < h0 \/ l <= x < h) by xomega.
Lemma add_ok: forall s, ok s -> forall l0 h0, l0 < h0 -> ok (add l0 h0 s).

Fixpoint remove (L H: Z) (s: t) {struct s} : t := match s with | Nil => Nil | Cons l h s' => if zlt h L then Cons l h (remove L H s') else if zlt H l then s else if zlt l L then if zlt H h then Cons l L (Cons H h s') else Cons l L (remove L H s') else if zlt H h then Cons H h s' else remove L H s' end.
Lemma In_remove: forall x l0 h0 s, ok s -> (In x (remove l0 h0 s) <-> ~(l0 <= x < h0) /\ In x s).
Lemma remove_ok: forall l0 h0, l0 < h0 -> forall s, ok s -> ok (remove l0 h0 s).
rewrite In_remove in H1 by auto.

Fixpoint inter (s1 s2: t) {struct s1} : t := let fix intr (s2: t) : t := match s1, s2 with | Nil, _ => Nil | _, Nil => Nil | Cons l1 h1 s1', Cons l2 h2 s2' => if zle h1 l2 then inter s1' s2 else if zle h2 l1 then intr s2' else if zle l1 l2 then if zle h2 h1 then Cons l2 h2 (intr s2') else Cons l2 h1 (inter s1' s2) else if zle h1 h2 then Cons l1 h1 (inter s1' s2) else Cons l1 h2 (intr s2') end in intr s2.
Lemma In_inter: forall x s1, ok s1 -> forall s2, ok s2 -> (In x (inter s1 s2) <-> In x s1 /\ In x s2).
assert (ok (Cons l h s)) by (constructor; auto).
assert (ok (Cons l0 h0 s0)) by (constructor; auto).
Lemma inter_ok: forall s1, ok s1 -> forall s2, ok s2 -> ok (inter s1 s2).
assert (In x (inter (Cons l h s) s0)) by exact H3.
assert (In x (inter (Cons l h s) s0)) by exact H3.
Fixpoint union (s1 s2: t) : t := match s1, s2 with | Nil, _ => s2 | _, Nil => s1 | Cons l1 h1 s1', Cons l2 h2 s2' => add l1 h1 (add l2 h2 (union s1' s2')) end.
Lemma In_ok_union: forall s1, ok s1 -> forall s2, ok s2 -> ok (union s1 s2) /\ (forall x, In x s1 \/ In x s2 <-> In x (union s1 s2)).
Fixpoint beq (s1 s2: t) : bool := match s1, s2 with | Nil, Nil => true | Cons l1 h1 t1, Cons l2 h2 t2 => zeq l1 l2 && zeq h1 h2 && beq t1 t2 | _, _ => false end.
Lemma beq_spec: forall s1, ok s1 -> forall s2, ok s2 -> (beq s1 s2 = true <-> (forall x, In x s1 <-> In x s2)).
rewrite IHok in H3 by auto.
Definition t := { r: R.t | R.ok r }.
Program Definition In (x: Z) (s: t) := R.In x s.
Theorem In_empty: forall x, ~(In x empty).
Program Definition interval (l h: Z) : t := if zlt l h then R.Cons l h R.Nil else R.Nil.
Theorem In_interval: forall x l h, In x (interval l h) <-> l <= x < h.
unfold In, interval; destruct (zlt l h); simpl.
Program Definition add (l h: Z) (s: t) : t := if zlt l h then R.add l h s else s.
Theorem In_add: forall x l h s, In x (add l h s) <-> l <= x < h \/ In x s.
Program Definition remove (l h: Z) (s: t) : t := if zlt l h then R.remove l h s else s.
Theorem In_remove: forall x l h s, In x (remove l h s) <-> ~(l <= x < h) /\ In x s.
Program Definition inter (s1 s2: t) : t := R.inter s1 s2.
Theorem In_inter: forall x s1 s2, In x (inter s1 s2) <-> In x s1 /\ In x s2.
Program Definition union (s1 s2: t) : t := R.union s1 s2.
Theorem In_union: forall x s1 s2, In x (union s1 s2) <-> In x s1 \/ In x s2.
Program Definition mem (x: Z) (s: t) := R.mem x s.
Theorem mem_spec: forall x s, mem x s = true <-> In x s.
Program Definition contains (l h: Z) (s: t) := if zlt l h then R.contains l h s else true.
Theorem contains_spec: forall l h s, contains l h s = true <-> (forall x, l <= x < h -> In x s).
Program Definition beq (s1 s2: t) : bool := R.beq s1 s2.
Theorem beq_spec: forall s1 s2, beq s1 s2 = true <-> (forall x, In x s1 <-> In x s2).
